divs: Sighting DetailsWell,i was out side my house,clear day .Ilooked up and was looking at a passenger jet in the distance{contrails].Thats when i noticed a small very very shinny like sunshine on polished chrome,real bright comming towards me,{in my direction]i ran inside and grabed my kodak cx7430 4.0 mega pixels .the object then made a smooth sweeping turn headed south.the photos i have sent are outside my house.I did not see the other object in photo lower left ,till i looked at photos on comp. WOW.Ive sent same report to U.F.O.s north west.but to my suprize, not one person has said anything about my post,i mean if anything its military and id say no jet ,is going to touch this. of course,im guessing.the other object i got two photos of [i did not see at time of taking photos of main object]But clearly its following first object.I dont know it just was gone, i was exited but i did get some evidence of high tech wonder machines.
